This paper deals with the problem of leader selection in multi-agent systems, which is a core topic in the field of multi-agent systems (MAS). Therefore, the most likely category for this paper is cs.MA (Multiagent Systems). 

The paper also deals with the optimization of the total mean-square error of the follower agent states, which is a problem in control theory. Therefore, the paper may also belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control). 

The paper uses optimization techniques to solve the leader selection problem, which is a topic in optimization theory. Therefore, the paper may also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.IT (Information Theory).
